name: Froggy (Galactic Software)
overview: Not to be confused with Froggy from Krypton Force (which is also a Frogger clone) Froggy from Galactic Software has the same premise: Cross the frog over to the other side of the screen while avoiding cars, trucks, snakes, etc. The Galactic Software game does, however, have slightly more simplified graphics than the game from Krypton Force.
